#: ../../concepts.rst:2
msgid "核心概念"
msgstr "Core Concepts"

#: ../../concepts.rst:4
msgid "本部分解释 AgentSociety 2 的核心概念。"
msgstr "This section explains the core concepts of AgentSociety 2."

#: ../../concepts.rst:7
msgid "架构概述"
msgstr "Architecture Overview"

#: ../../concepts.rst:9
msgid "AgentSociety 2 围绕三个主要组件构建："
msgstr "AgentSociety 2 is built around three main components:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:11
msgid "**智能体 (Agents)**: 使用 LLM 与环境交互的自主实体"
msgstr "**Agents**: Autonomous entities that use LLMs to interact with environments"

#: ../../concepts.rst:12
msgid "**环境模块 (Environment Modules)**: 定义模拟规则的可组合组件"
msgstr "**Environment Modules**: Composable components that define simulation rules"

#: ../../concepts.rst:13
msgid "**AgentSociety**: 管理智能体和环境的协调器"
msgstr "**AgentSociety**: Coordinator that manages agents and environments"

#: ../../concepts.rst:32
msgid "智能体-环境接口"
msgstr "Agent-Environment Interface"

#: ../../concepts.rst:34
msgid "智能体通过两个主要方法与环境交互："
msgstr "Agents interact with environments through two main methods:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:36
msgid "**ask()**: 查询或观察环境状态"
msgstr "**ask()**: Query or observe environment state"

#: ../../concepts.rst:37
msgid "**intervene()**: 修改环境状态"
msgstr "**intervene()**: Modify environment state"

#: ../../concepts.rst:39
msgid "这个统一接口允许智能体与任何环境模块自然通信。"
msgstr "This unified interface allows agents to communicate naturally with any environment module."

#: ../../concepts.rst:42
msgid "@tool 装饰器"
msgstr "The @tool Decorator"

#: ../../concepts.rst:44
msgid "环境模块通过 ``@tool`` 装饰器公开其功能："
msgstr "Environment modules expose their functionality through the ``@tool`` decorator:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:62
msgid "**参数：**"
msgstr "**Parameters:**"

#: ../../concepts.rst:64
msgid "``readonly`` (bool): 函数是否修改状态 * ``True`` = 只读观察 * ``False`` = 修改环境"
msgstr "``readonly`` (bool): Whether the function modifies state * ``True`` = read-only, can be used in queries * ``False`` = modifies state, can be used in interventions"

#: ../../concepts.rst:68
msgid "``kind`` (str): 用于优化的函数类别 * ``\"observe\"``: 单参数观察 * ``\"statistics\"``: 聚合查询（无参数） * ``None``: 常规工具"
msgstr "``kind`` (str): The type of tool * ``\"observe\"``: Single-parameter observations (requires readonly=True) * ``\"statistics\"``: Aggregate queries (no parameters, requires readonly=True) * ``None`` or omitted: Regular tool (any signature, any readonly value)"

#: ../../concepts.rst:74
msgid "CodeGenRouter"
msgstr "CodeGenRouter"

#: ../../concepts.rst:76
msgid "CodeGenRouter 通过以下方式将智能体连接到环境模块："
msgstr "CodeGenRouter connects agents to environment modules by:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:78
msgid "从环境模块中提取工具签名"
msgstr "Extracting tool signatures from environment modules"

#: ../../concepts.rst:79
msgid "根据智能体输入生成调用适当工具的代码"
msgstr "Generating code to call appropriate tools based on agent input"

#: ../../concepts.rst:80
msgid "在沙盒环境中安全执行代码"
msgstr "Safely executing code in a sandboxed environment"

#: ../../concepts.rst:81
msgid "将结果返回给智能体"
msgstr "Returning results to the agent"

#: ../../concepts.rst:83
msgid "这种方法允许智能体与任何环境模块组合交互，而无需更改代码。"
msgstr "This approach allows agents to interact with any combination of environment modules without code changes."

